### Get all meals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meals

### Get meal by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meals/1

### Create a meal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pasta Bolognese",
  "calories": 650,
  "protein": 30.5,
  "fat": 20.0,
  "carbs": 80.0,
  "date": "2025-01-15"
}

### Update a meal
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/meals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pasta Bolognese",
  "calories": 700,
  "protein": 32.0,
  "fat": 22.0,
  "carbs": 82.0,
  "date": "2025-01-15"
}

### Delete a meal
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/meals/1
